            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "No more flaky patches",
            "review_text": "Living in an air-conditioned office all day made my skin so dry that even expensive creams didn’t help. NutraDew works differently, ceramides repair the skin barrier while hyaluronic acid holds on to the moisture. Now my skin stays smooth and hydrated all day, and my makeup doesn’t crack around my eyes",
            "name": "Nutradew Customer",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_hTTJYV": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_27_2025_04_59_10_PM.png",
            "name-person": "Sameeth K",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "Confidence Without Makeup",
            "review_text": "I’ve had uneven skin tone for years, and it always made me pile on concealer. After using Melt n Glo for 3 months, I’ve been going makeup-free more often. My skin looks more even, has a natural glow, and feels smoother. The mix of glutathione, pomegranate extract, vitamin E, and zinc really seems to be nourishing from the inside.",
            "name": "Melt N Glo Customer",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_Ejpnjb": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_27_2025_04_59_10_PM.png",
            "name-person": "Nandini Gowda",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "My Go-To for Dull Skin Days",
            "review_text": "I work long hours, and my skin used to look flat and lifeless. Melt n Glo has been a game-changer. The combination of glutathione, marigold extract, vitamin C, and selenium is giving me brightness I didn’t know I could get. Even my hyperpigmentation marks are less noticeable now. It’s so easy to take daily, no pills or mixing powders",
            "name": "Melt N Glo Customer",
            "date": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_JnyPrc": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "stars": 5,
            "user_image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_27_2025_04_59_10_PM.png",
            "name-person": "Rajiv Rajan",
            "position": "",
            "stars_image": "shopify://shop_images/Golden-5-Star-Rating-PNG.png",
            "head_text": "Didn’t Think This Was for Guys, but…",
            "review_text": "I’ll be honest, I bought Melt n Glo because my wife kept telling me my skin looked “tired” and uneven. I wasn’t expecting much, but after about 10 weeks, even I can see the difference. My face looks fresher, the tan patches from old sun damage have lightened, and I don’t look like I’ve been pulling all-nighters anymore. Plus, it’s super easy to take, no pills, just melts on your tongue. I’m sticking with it. –",
            "name": "Melt N Glo Customer",
            "date": ""
          }
        }
